      <title>Disco Nap - Jeff&amp;#039;s ACWW Blog</title>
      <author>Jeff</author>
      <link>https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Aug 2025 03:57:31 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;article id="post-8343" class="post-8343 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized"&gt; 	&lt;header class="entry-header"&gt; 		&lt;h1 class="entry-title"&gt;Disco Nap&lt;/h1&gt;	&lt;/header&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-header --&gt;  	 	 	&lt;div class="entry-content"&gt; 		 &lt;p&gt;On Wednesday, I found Pascal standing near the shore. I spoke with him, and he told me that albatrosses aren&amp;#8217;t so bad once you get to know them.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img fetchpriority="high" width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Pascal: Albatrosses aren't so bad once you get to know 'em." class="wp-image-8344" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;He then gave me some sea view wallpaper before plunging into the sea.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;A message posted to the bulletin board gave tips on how to make food look more appealing. Although the tips aren&amp;#8217;t exactly earth-shattering news. 😛&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="-Talking to Myself- To make food look more appealing, use a nice dish and arrange the plate well! It's cheap and easy!" class="wp-image-8345" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Yesterday, Truffles told me how excited she is for the fireworks festival. But she wasn&amp;#8217;t sure that she could stay awake long enough, so she wondered if she should take a &amp;#8220;disco nap&amp;#8221; first. 🪩&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Truffles: Should I maybe take a disco nap during the day so that I can stay up late?" class="wp-image-8346" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Today, I met up with Truffles again outside of town hall. She started to tell me something about Pelly and Phyllis&amp;#8230;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Truffles: Hon! Can you believe Pelly and Phyllis are..." class="wp-image-8348" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;But she caught herself before revealing a &amp;#8220;scorching secret.&amp;#8221; And she blamed &lt;em&gt;me &lt;/em&gt;for her almost spilling the beans! I didn&amp;#8217;t say a thing.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Truffles: WHOA! You ALMOST got me to divulge that scorching secret! VERY SNEAKY of you!" class="wp-image-8349" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Truffles stomped over to the museum, where she met up with Whitney. Truffles (falsely) claimed that she was voted the most popular girl in Forest. Yeah, as if Whitney is going to believe that one. (Maybe when pigs fly.)&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Truffles: I've been voted the most popular girl in Forest!" class="wp-image-8350" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;But Whitney didn&amp;#8217;t go that direction. Instead, she told Truffles that when you&amp;#8217;re really popular, you&amp;#8217;re also really despised. 😆&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array" alt="Whitney: When you're popular, it means people secretly despise you." class="wp-image-8351" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;So Whitney convinced Truffles that she has to make people despise her, in order to get them to really &lt;em&gt;like &lt;/em&gt;her. These conversations are so crazy sometimes. 🤪&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Caroline is the latest villager to catch a cold, so I gave her some medicine yesterday and again today. Get well soon, Caroline!&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 	&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-content --&gt;  	&lt;footer class="entry-footer"&gt; 		&lt;span class="byline"&gt;&lt;img alt='' src='https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/Array' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49'/&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Author &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="author vcard"&gt;&lt;a class="url fn n" href="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/author/jvgsjeff/"&gt;Jeff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="posted-on"&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Posted on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2025/08/29/disco-nap/" rel="bookmark"&gt;&lt;time class="entry-date published" datetime="2025-08-29T23:57:31-04:00"&gt;August 29, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;time class="updated" datetime="2025-08-29T23:59:19-04:00"&gt;August 29, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;/footer&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-footer --&gt; &lt;/article&gt;</description>
